{
  "url": "https://www.hymnal.net/en/hymn/h/1298",
  "title": "Chosen by God in ages past",
  "verses": [
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "Chosen"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "by God in"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "ages"
            },
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "past,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "A",
              "text": "Our God"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "will"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "never"
            },
            {
              "chord": "A",
              "text": "let us"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "go;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Sal"
            },
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "vation"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D7",
              "text": "is as"
            },
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "sured fore'er;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "'Tis"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "such securi"
            },
            {
              "chord": "C",
              "text": "ty"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D7",
              "text": "we"
            },
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "know."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "1"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "“I give to them eternal life,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "They shall not perish,” is His word;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "“No one shall snatch them from Our hands,”"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "This is the promise of the Lord."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Yet there’s a word for God’s own sons,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Which is a warning from the Lord:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For those not ready when He comes,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "“Worse punishment” and not “reward.”"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Reward is not eternal life,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "It’s based on how we run the race;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "It all depends on what we build,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "It’s not a matter, here, of grace."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "’Tis for God’s kingdom we press on,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Like Moses, we are for the Lord;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We suffer with God’s people here"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And look away to the reward."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Richer by far, reproach of Christ,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Than Egypt’s treasures, which are sin;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "By faith we leave Egyptian land,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Avoiding next age discipline."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "6"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our soul gained for the kingdom’s age—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For this we lose our soul life here;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "If we lay down our soul life now,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’ll save it for Christ’s kingdom there."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "7"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We all must learn to pay the price,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Christ must be worked into our soul;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "’Tis thus our soul is gained by Him,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "This is our aim and this our goal."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "8"
    }
  ],
